SUMMARY:DBS: Prepare\, then capture one real client concern
DESCRIPTION:Review one resource and decide which client concern it helps y
 ou address. Then write down one real client objection in the client's own 
 words — don't solve it yet\, just capture it clearly so you can respond 
 more effectively next time.
